"{\n  \"story\": {\n    \"name\": \"Overview\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2023-12-13T11:06:03.084Z\",\n    \"published_at\": \"2024-11-27T11:34:13.154Z\",\n    \"updated_at\": \"2024-11-27T11:34:13.197Z\",\n    \"id\": 418384767,\n    \"uuid\": \"3c36b8b0-b0f2-4e80-8a11-862c1f624796\",\n    \"content\": {\n      \"seo\": {\n        \"_uid\": \"1fb424ab-10d5-4f70-9805-d74a8c533db4\",\n        \"title\": \"Talent 2024-2025 – Digital Exhibition | Foam: All about photography\",\n        \"plugin\": \"seo_metatags\",\n        \"og_image\": \"https://a.storyblok.com/f/113697/1029x1456/8adc868142/overview_asset_2.jpg\",\n        \"og_title\": \"Talent 2024-2025 | Digital Exhibition – Foam: All about photography\",\n        \"description\": \"Foam proudly presents 20 Talents selected for Foam Talent 2024-2025 in this interactive digital exhibition, highlighting the connections and unique artistic viewpoints.\",\n        \"twitter_image\": \"https://a.storyblok.com/f/113697/1029x1456/8adc868142/overview_asset_2.jpg\",\n        \"twitter_title\": \"Talent 2024-2025 | Digital Exhibition – Foam: All about photography\",\n        \"og_description\": \"Foam proudly presents 20 Talents selected for Foam Talent 2024-2025 in this interactive digital exhibition, highlighting the connections and unique artistic viewpoints.\",\n        \"twitter_description\": \"Foam proudly presents 20 Talents selected for Foam Talent 2024-2025 in this interactive digital exhibition, highlighting the connections and unique artistic viewpoints.\"\n      },\n      \"_uid\": \"a00898ee-3904-4bb5-ab45-dadba4a1a833\",\n      \"component\": \"Talent2024OverviewPage\",\n      \"copyright\": \"All image content on talent.foam.org are courtesy of the artists.\",\n      \"introText\": \"artists shaping the future of photography\",\n      \"asideTitle\": \"selected artists\",\n      \"description\": {\n        \"type\": \"doc\",\n        \"content\": [\n          {\n            \"type\": \"heading\",\n            \"attrs\": {\n              \"level\": 1\n            },\n            \"content\": [\n              {\n                \"text\": \"Welcome to Talent 2024-2025 – the digital exhibition.\",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"italic\"\n                  },\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              },\n              {\n                \"text\": \" \",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              },\n              {\n                \"text\": \" \",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"type\": \"heading\",\n            \"attrs\": {\n              \"level\": 1\n            },\n            \"content\": [\n              {\n                \"text\": \"Here, Foam proudly presents 20 selected Talents in their very own online universe. Out of a dazzling 2,480 submissions, this final curation of exceptional work defines the new horizons of the medium of photography, thematically and technically. Highlighting the connections, this interactive network brings all Talents together and maps out their distinct artistic viewpoints.\",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              },\n              {\n                \"text\": \" \",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"type\": \"paragraph\",\n            \"content\": [\n              {\n                \"text\": \"Spanning across the globe, the stories told by these artists reflect a universal yearning for belonging—a profound desire to anchor, to establish a connection with the past and carve out a sense of place. A driving force underpinning their work is the quest to trace heritage, untangle family lines, and explore personal identity.\",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              },\n              {\n                \"text\": \" \",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"type\": \"paragraph\",\n            \"content\": [\n              {\n                \"text\": \"Acknowledging the constructed nature of history, memory, or even their own thoughts, these artists boldly confront existing narratives. They embark on a journey of unlearning, challenging established stories, and turn to the expansive nature of photography to build new understandings and narratives, resonating more authentically with their lived experiences.\",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              },\n              {\n                \"text\": \" \",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"rgb(0, 0, 0)\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"type\": \"paragraph\",\n            \"content\": [\n              {\n                \"text\": \"Noteworthy in their approach is the harmonious balance between tradition and innovation. The artists seamlessly blend traditional photographic techniques with cutting-edge developments, including the much-discussed realm of artificial intelligence, and other mediums such as moving image, embroidery and music. \",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              },\n              {\n                \"text\": \"Select one of the filters to zoom in on these different techniques and mediums.\",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"italic\"\n                  },\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              },\n              {\n                \"text\": \" \",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"rgb(255, 0, 0)\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"type\": \"paragraph\",\n            \"content\": [\n              {\n                \"text\": \"This digital exhibition presents the work in a truly multi-medial way, inviting you to \",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              },\n              {\n                \"text\": \"look\",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"italic\"\n                  },\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              },\n              {\n                \"text\": \", \",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n                      \"color\": \"\"\n                    }\n                  }\n                ]\n              },\n              {\n                \"text\": \"listen \",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"marks\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"italic\"\n                  },\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"textStyle\",\n                    \"attrs\": {\n       